      "A new attacker calls `provideLiquidity` while `pool.totalLiquidity` is depressed, minting inflated LP shares",
      "The orderbook later calls `receiveETHFromOrderbook` and/or `receiveTokenFromOrderbook` to return the borrowed assets",
      "The attacker withdraws and receives a share of those returned assets despite not funding the original exposure"
